<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/AboutUs.css">
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        /* Container */
        .containers {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

      

        /* About Us Section */
        .about-us {
            padding: 40px 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .about-us .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-us h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .about-us p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
        }

        .about-us h3 {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .about-us .team {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .about-us .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 250px;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .about-us .team-member img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-us .team-member h4 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        .about-us .team-member p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        footer .social-media {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        footer .social-media li {
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        footer .social-media li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        footer .social-media li a:hover {
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/header') %> <!-- Include your header from a partial -->

    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="containers">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Go-&gt;Cab, your trusted partner in ride-sharing. We are committed to providing safe, reliable, and affordable transportation solutions to our customers. Our mission is to make your travel experience as seamless and enjoyable as possible.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>At Go-&gt;Cab, our mission is to revolutionize the way people travel by offering a user-friendly platform that connects riders and drivers. We strive to offer a service that is not only convenient but also reliable and affordable, ensuring that your journey is smooth and stress-free.</p>
            
            <h3>Meet Our Team</h3>
            <div class="team">
                <div class="team-member">
                   
                    <h4>Bahaar Sharma</h4>
                    <p>Co-Founder & CEO</p>
                    <p>Bahaar is the visionary behind Go-&gt;Cab, with years of experience in the transportation industry.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                   
                    <h4>Bhumi Alhawat</h4>
                    <p>Chief Operating Officer</p>
                    <p>Bhumi oversees the day-to-day operations, ensuring everything runs smoothly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                
                    <h4>Arsh Sudan</h4>
                    <p>Founder</p>
                    <p>Arsh oversees the day-to-day operations, ensuring everything runs smoothly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Go-&gt;Cab. All rights reserved.</p>
            <ul class="social-media">
                <li><a href="#">Facebook</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
